                    i.far.fa-star      
                    i.far.fa-star      
                  span.reviewAuthor  Patrick Mahomes
                  small.reviewTimestamp  2 February 2020
                .col-12
                  p It was okay. Coffee wasn't great. Definitely not Whataburger!
    .col-12.col-lg-3
        p.lead
              | McDonald's is on Loc8r because it has accessible wifi and space to sit down with your laptop and get some work done.
        p
              | If you've been and you like it - or if you don't - please leave a review to help other people just like you.